    "discriminators": [
     "The extreme end of the broadband-roar family: everything AIRCRAFT-JET is, but louder, lower and flatter. root_mean_square_level ~0.38, low_band_energy ~0.60, and crest_factor down at ~3.4 because a saturated roar has almost no peak-to-RMS headroom left. Combustion instability is stochastic, so onset_periodicity stays near zero exactly as it does for a jet.",
     "Against AIRCRAFT-JET: a matter of degree on level and LF weight, not a change of morphology — narrowable, not separable. Most library rockets are designed/processed anyway, which further erodes any physical claim.",
     "Against a true EXPLOSION burst: a rocket SUSTAINS. A slow envelope_attack_seconds (~0.6 s) held over tens of seconds rules out a single transient, and the length gate enforces it."
    ],
